title: Lootere
subTitle: Police inspectors Karan and Ali investigate the murder of a colleague, Inspector Rane. Karan takes the responsibility of protecting Anjali, a bar dancer who is a key witness to the crime.

title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Durga, who is blind, loses her fiance, Rohit, while she is getting her eye surgery. As she copes with her pain, she finds solace in Raj but chaos ensues when Rohit returns from the dead.

title: Phamous
subTitle: Radhe looks up to Kadak Singh, a local politician, but holds a grudge against his partner, Ram Tripathi. However, things reach a boiling point when Tripathi sets his sights on Radhe's wife, Lalli.

title: Raja Saab
subTitle: Upon Prince Pratap's insistence, Rajoo impersonates him in front of Princess Poonam. But the imitation lands him in trouble when she starts falling for Rajoo, unaware of his poor background.

title: Do Chor
subTitle: Tony, a burglar, comes under the radar of suspicion when a series of mysterious thefts bewilder the police. Soon enough, he tries to redeem his honour by going after the real criminal.

title: Gair Kaanooni
subTitle: Police Inspector Kapil Khanna realises that his baby boy has been switched with a girl child by the hospital and files a lawsuit against the owner, Robert Decosta while trying to find his missing son.

title: Ekka Raja Rani
subTitle: Talented dancer, Barkha, saves the life of an underground crime boss, VK, who offers her a job as repayment. Later VK falls for Barkha, but she is in love with another man.

title: I M 24
subTitle: A 42-year-old writer falls in love with a 22-year-old beauty queen. However, things get complicated when his roommate encourages him to make up stories to impress her.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Albela
subTitle: A woman gets stuck in India when her flight to a foreign country gets delayed. While travelling in India, she meets Tony, a tour guide, and things take a turn when he falls in love with her.

title: Albela
subTitle: A woman gets stuck in India when her flight to a foreign country gets delayed. While travelling in India, she meets Tony, a tour guide, and things take a turn when he falls in love with her.

title: Maharathi
subTitle: After his boss, Jai Singh, commits suicide, Subhash, a chauffeur, conspires to get his insurance money. He then teams up with Jai's wife, Mallika, to make the suicide look like a well-planned murder.

title: Waqt Ki Awaz
subTitle: A rich girl runs away from home and settles down with a truck driver. However, her dream life is shattered when she learns that her new lover has been accused of murder.

title: Har Dil Jo Pyar Karega
subTitle: Raj, an aspiring singer, rescues Pooja, the daughter of a wealthy man, from an accident. However, he soon finds himself in a web of complications when he falls in love with her best friend.

title: Dulaara
subTitle: Falsely accused of murder, Raja becomes a target for Vijay, a police inspector and his lover's brother. In a bid to end his misery and catch the real culprit, Raja sets out on a mission.

title: Firaaq
subTitle: In the aftermath of Gujarat's violent 2002 riots, victims find their lives changed forever and reel from the deep impact the upheaval left on them.

title: Gundaraj
subTitle: Ajay and Pooja fall in love and decide to get married. To earn money and get settled, Ajay applies for a job in Bombay, but is framed in a rape case and is imprisoned for four years.

title: Achanak
subTitle: A man is determined to prove his lover's innocence after she is suddenly accused of murdering his family.

title: Raja
subTitle: Raju and Madhu are forced apart by the latter's elder brothers, leading to increased distance between the two.

title: Mohra
subTitle: After a journalist helps to release him from prison, a man agrees to work as a hitman for her, leading him to entangle with a battle between two drug lords.

title: Mohra
subTitle: After a journalist helps to release him from prison, a man agrees to work as a hitman for her, leading him to entangle with a battle between two drug lords.

title: Fun2shh... Dudes in the 10th Century
subTitle: Three men are accused of stealing a crown and whilst on the run, they are transported to the 10th century. Amidst several adventures, they must try to bring the crown back to prove their innocence.

title: Ekkees Tareekh Shubh Muhurat
subTitle: Pandit Girdhari Laal Sharma wants to get his daughter, Radha, married extravagantly but lacks the money for it. He then devises a plan to source the money, unaware of the consequences.

title: Jhoothi
subTitle: Kalpana, a habitual liar, attempts to sabotage her sister's arranged marriage to a doctor, but complications arise when she develops feelings for him.

title: Ujala Hi Ujala
subTitle: Anuradha's stepmother forces her to consume alcohol and she becomes an addict. After her father's death, she takes over the business and falls in love with Vikram, but her happiness is short-lived.

title: Nakshatra
subTitle: An aspiring screenwriter becomes involved in a diamond heist while writing a script for his film and struggles to evade the police.

title: Buddha Mil Gaya
subTitle: Two unsuspecting blokes find themselves entangled in a sinister web of intrigue after harbouring a mysterious millionaire.

title: Bumper Draw
subTitle: Two men form a friendship in the most unlikely situation. Later, when they meet a rich man, they begin to devise a plan that will put an end to their financial difficulties.

title: Chal Mere Bhai
subTitle: Destiny entangles Sapna with a bereaved Vicky and his fun-loving younger brother Prem Oberoi in a tapestry of romance, heartbreak, and sacrifice.

title: Hum Hain Rahi Pyar Ke
subTitle: Rahul looks after his spoilt nephews, Sunny and Vicky, and niece, Munni. When they go to a funfair, they meet Vyjayanti, who has run away from home, and decide to shelter her without Rahul's consent.

title: Bheja Fry 2
subTitle: Bhushan, a tax inspector, meets Ajit, a businessman evading an IT raid, on a cruise ship. In a bizarre turn of events, Ajit and Bhushan get lost on an isolated island.
